# Powerboat Show Lead Generation Funnel - Complete Setup Guide

## Overview
This system captures leads with a free boat show guide, then upsells them to a $9.99/month newsletter subscription via PayPal.

---

## üì¶ What You've Received

1. **Landing Page** (`index.html`) - Main opt-in page for free guide
2. **Thank You Page** (`thank-you.html`) - Download delivery + newsletter upsell
3. **Sample Newsletter** (`newsletter-sample.html`) - Preview of paid content
4. **Setup Instructions** (this document)

---

## üöÄ Quick Start Checklist

- [ ] Set up PayPal subscription plan
