## 4Ô∏è‚É£ Web Hosting Setup

### Option A: Shared Hosting (Recommended for Beginners)

**Recommended Hosts:**
- Bluehost ($3-5/month)
- SiteGround ($4-7/month)
- HostGator ($3-6/month)

**Setup Steps:**
1. Purchase hosting plan with domain
2. Access cPanel or hosting dashboard
3. Use File Manager or FTP
4. Upload all HTML files to `public_html` folder
5. Upload PDF to same folder

### Option B: Free Hosting (Testing)

**Netlify (Free):**
1. Sign up at netlify.com
2. Drag and drop your files
3. Get free subdomain: `yoursite.netlify.app`
4. Custom domain available with upgrade

**GitHub Pages (Free):**
1. Create GitHub account
2. Create new repository
3. Upload files
4. Enable GitHub Pages in settings

### File Structure
```
public_html/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.html (landing page)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ thank-you.html
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ newsletter-sample.html
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ privacy-policy.html
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ powerboat-guide-2025.pdf
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ images/ (if you add any)
```

