## 5Ô∏è‚É£ Domain & DNS Setup

### Domain Registration
- **Namecheap** ($8-15/year)
- **Google Domains** ($12/year)
- **Domain.com** ($10-15/year)

### Good Domain Examples
- PowerboatShowInsider.com
- AnnapolisBoatGuide.com
- USPowerboatShow.com (check availability)

### DNS Configuration
Point your domain to your hosting:
1. Log into domain registrar
2. Find DNS settings
3. Update nameservers to your host's nameservers
4. Wait 24-48 hours for propagation

