## 6Ô∏è‚É£ Analytics & Tracking

### Google Analytics Setup

1. **Create Account**
   - Go to analytics.google.com
   - Set up property for your website

2. **Add Tracking Code**
   
   Add this before `</head>` in all HTML files:
   
   ```html
   <!-- Google Analytics -->
   <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-XXXXXXXXXX"></script>
   <script>
     window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
     function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
     gtag('js', new Date());
     gtag('config', 'G-XXXXXXXXXX');
   </script>
   ```

3. **Set Up Goals**
   - Goal 1: Form submission (landing page)
   - Goal 2: PDF download click
   - Goal 3: PayPal subscribe click

### Facebook Pixel (Optional)

If running Facebook ads:
1. Create pixel in Facebook Events Manager
2. Add pixel code to all pages
3. Set up custom conversions

