## 8Ô∏è‚É£ Legal Requirements

### Privacy Policy

You'll need to add a privacy policy page. Here's what to include:

**Information Collection:**
- What data you collect (name, email)
- How you use it (send guide, newsletter)
- How you store it
- Third parties (Mailchimp, PayPal)

**User Rights:**
- Right to unsubscribe
- Right to data deletion
- Contact information

**Tools to Generate:**
- TermsFeed.com (free generator)
- PrivacyPolicies.com
- Consult with lawyer for compliance

### GDPR Compliance (If targeting EU)
- Add cookie consent banner
- Include GDPR-compliant privacy policy
- Allow easy data deletion requests

### CAN-SPAM Compliance
- Include physical mailing address
- Add clear unsubscribe link
- Honor unsubscribe requests within 10 days

